id: pm-mpmv
title: Align default item types with Decision tracking guidance
description: "Current runtime create/type contracts include Chore,Epic,Event,Feature,Issue,Meeting,Milestone,Reminder,Task but exclude Decision, while repository operating guidance explicitly expects decision artifacts. This mismatch creates first-run governance friction for agent workflows."
type: Issue
status: open
priority: 1
tags[5]: agent-ux,external-audit,governance,item-types,pm-cli
created_at: "2026-04-26T09:56:45.340Z"
updated_at: "2026-04-26T09:57:31.949Z"
assignee: codex-agent
author: codex-agent
estimated_minutes: 120
acceptance_criteria: "Default type guidance is consistent: either include Decision in the default runtime type registry/contracts or update bootstrap guidance to auto-provision Decision with clear examples."
parent: pm-r15d
